graphs.name: Communication Intelligence Extractor
graphs.description: Monitors Slack conversations to extract key decisions, issues, and insights, then maps them to relevant systems and processes. Captures organizational knowledge from informal communications.

graphs.name: Architecture Analysis Agent
graphs.description: Analyzes system architecture for complexity, dependencies, technical debt, and optimization opportunities. Maps architectural decisions to business outcomes and team productivity.

graphs.name: System Log Monitor Agent
graphs.description: Monitors system logs, error patterns, and performance metrics to identify issues, trends, and optimization opportunities. Maps incidents to system dependencies and business impact.

graphs.name: Decision Analysis Agent
graphs.description: Evaluates build-versus-buy decisions by analyzing technical requirements, team capabilities, timeline constraints, and total cost of ownership. Maps decision impacts across your system architecture.

graphs.name: Market Research Agent
graphs.description: Analyzes market landscapes, competitor positioning, and technology trends to identify opportunities and threats in your business domain. Maps market dynamics to your system architecture and business processes.

graphs.name: Connections Mapper
graphs.description: Interactive process that discovers, validates, and creates connections between systems through dependency analysis and data flow identification

graphs.name: Incremental System Discovery
graphs.description: Conversational flow that identifies and integrates new systems into existing workspace architecture through targeted questioning and dependency analysis.

graphs.name: Initialize workspace
graphs.description: discovers and maps your digital environment by creating entities, processes, and systems along with their interconnections. Generates business-specific attributes and metadata tailored to your organizational context, establishing a foundational knowledge graph for downstream automation and analysis

graphs.name: Domain Attributes builder
graphs.description: Takes context as input along with entity information (Core Entities, Systems) and extends the domain by identifying and mapping data structures.

graphs.name: Attribute Enhancement Agent
graphs.description: Identifies and adds business-specific metadata, tags, and custom properties to existing entities and systems. Adapts organizational taxonomies and domain-specific classifications to enrich your knowledge graph with contextual business intelligence.

graphs.name: System Intelligence Agent
graphs.description: Enables natural language querying across your mapped digital systems and connections. Analyzes relationships, dependencies, and data flows to provide actionable insights about system performance, integration bottlenecks, and architectural patterns within your environment.
